WEBVTT

bc1a5d4d-f1d8-4479-9e15-e4fd54ce212a-0
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.075
With the way a lot of work gets
done today, it's important to

bc1a5d4d-f1d8-4479-9e15-e4fd54ce212a-1
00:00:04.075 --> 00:00:06.852
know how to collaborate with
others using digital tools

bc1a5d4d-f1d8-4479-9e15-e4fd54ce212a-2
00:00:06.852 --> 00:00:07.200
online.

9628045d-2599-4323-b22a-e012a9d1fc0e-0
00:00:07.880 --> 00:00:11.268
With Microsoft Word, you can
share your document with others

9628045d-2599-4323-b22a-e012a9d1fc0e-1
00:00:11.268 --> 00:00:14.880
so they can view, comment on, or
coauthor the contents with you.

abfe93fd-9521-4f06-8b61-ec293599aaab-0
00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:18.427
This allows everyone to work on
the same document instead of

abfe93fd-9521-4f06-8b61-ec293599aaab-1
00:00:18.427 --> 00:00:21.572
multiple copies of the document,
so you never have to worry about

abfe93fd-9521-4f06-8b61-ec293599aaab-2
00:00:21.572 --> 00:00:24.479
changes or edits appearing in
some copies but not in others.

08b8fe16-6069-4d93-b291-efecb204c1b2-0
00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:28.638
When you share a Word document
for collaboration, everyone can

08b8fe16-6069-4d93-b291-efecb204c1b2-1
00:00:28.638 --> 00:00:30.850
work on and see changes at the
same time.

3a27da12-52af-447f-8a79-5a4892fa9c69-0
00:00:31.930 --> 00:00:34.697
To share a document, open it in
Word and then click the Share

3a27da12-52af-447f-8a79-5a4892fa9c69-1
00:00:34.697 --> 00:00:35.010
button.

2aa1cb0f-0058-4c4a-8c94-78597739e890-0
00:00:36.010 --> 00:00:37.890
From here you'll save it to your
OneDrive account.

924247ba-748a-403d-bf96-4bc55c164452-0
00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:40.600
This laces the document in the
cloud so it can be easily

924247ba-748a-403d-bf96-4bc55c164452-1
00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:42.530
accessed by everyone who needs
to work on it.

0c3d80c5-c8d0-4c04-a6f6-3cd6f97be1de-0
00:00:43.010 --> 00:00:45.610
Next, you'll determine the
ermissions for the file notice.

12468f88-d1d7-4ef4-9996-74716e2e0787-0
00:00:45.610 --> 00:00:48.330
By default it says anyone with
the link can edit this file.

f83e59e3-d8da-43b0-80c6-1f6e7aa3baa6-0
00:00:48.810 --> 00:00:51.682
If you need to share a document
with people, but you only want

f83e59e3-d8da-43b0-80c6-1f6e7aa3baa6-1
00:00:51.682 --> 00:00:54.645
them to be able to read it, you
can click here and uncheck Allow

f83e59e3-d8da-43b0-80c6-1f6e7aa3baa6-2
00:00:54.645 --> 00:00:55.010
editing.

c98a8567-dcf7-4da3-aa10-2cd0fdde9ed7-0
00:00:55.730 --> 00:00:58.462
Additionally, you can set an
expiration date so the document

c98a8567-dcf7-4da3-aa10-2cd0fdde9ed7-1
00:00:58.462 --> 00:01:01.239
won't be able to be accessed
after the secified date, and you

c98a8567-dcf7-4da3-aa10-2cd0fdde9ed7-2
00:01:01.239 --> 00:01:03.927
can also password protected the
document so only people you

c98a8567-dcf7-4da3-aa10-2cd0fdde9ed7-3
00:01:03.927 --> 00:01:06.570
share the password with will be
able to open the document.

75cffacd-bb28-453e-8b98-b41dacb2a739-0
00:01:06.570 --> 00:01:09.556
I'm going to click cancel for
now because I do want to allow

75cffacd-bb28-453e-8b98-b41dacb2a739-1
00:01:09.556 --> 00:01:12.690
editing and I don't need to set
an expiration date or password.

52b167cc-499c-4163-ac4f-7fdcd719ea7d-0
00:01:13.490 --> 00:01:15.590
Next, you'll enter the e-mail
addresses of the people you want

52b167cc-499c-4163-ac4f-7fdcd719ea7d-1
00:01:15.590 --> 00:01:16.490
to share the document with.

3f6465f4-06af-4fb2-8d70-106d1533ef87-0
00:01:16.490 --> 00:01:18.850
I'm going to share this with my
colleague Jade.

534cf0fb-e411-4d3e-aae7-8ac88938ece0-0
00:01:19.530 --> 00:01:21.907
Her name and e-mail appears
here, so I'll select it and you

534cf0fb-e411-4d3e-aae7-8ac88938ece0-1
00:01:21.907 --> 00:01:23.730
can share it with as many people
as you like.

a02e70f8-102e-4170-ae39-8e38585459c1-0
00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:27.958
You can add a message to explain
why you're sharing the document,

a02e70f8-102e-4170-ae39-8e38585459c1-1
00:01:27.958 --> 00:01:28.840
then click Send.

b2700158-6d8c-4371-a27e-f7da871c547a-0
00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:32.161
Microsoft will send an e-mail
that includes a link to the

b2700158-6d8c-4371-a27e-f7da871c547a-1
00:01:32.161 --> 00:01:33.360
document to your recipients.

0bc30549-a71d-45d4-ac32-fe2bfd6d8d88-0
00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.280
Let's see what this looks like
from the perspective of someone

0bc30549-a71d-45d4-ac32-fe2bfd6d8d88-1
00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:37.040
receiving the e-mail.

ba73621c-5720-4c7a-8463-13181fc1e7b2-0
00:01:37.760 --> 00:01:40.833
I'm actually logged into Jade's
e-mail here, and here's the

ba73621c-5720-4c7a-8463-13181fc1e7b2-1
00:01:40.833 --> 00:01:41.960
e-mail from Microsoft.

6d9c0725-6178-4e4a-9d75-4a45a0c92a22-0
00:01:42.480 --> 00:01:45.116
And here she can click Open to
open the document in Word

6d9c0725-6178-4e4a-9d75-4a45a0c92a22-1
00:01:45.116 --> 00:01:45.440
Online.

7ad9822d-3ae6-4986-b157-18e243889b14-0
00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:48.840
To edit the document, she clicks
Edit Document.

1834d8b1-4af1-4932-b86f-bd53e02c70b4-0
00:01:49.370 --> 00:01:51.775
She'll have the choice of
editing it here in Word Online,

1834d8b1-4af1-4932-b86f-bd53e02c70b4-1
00:01:51.775 --> 00:01:53.891
or she can use the desktop
version of Word if it's

1834d8b1-4af1-4932-b86f-bd53e02c70b4-2
00:01:53.891 --> 00:01:54.970
installed on her computer.

b337d443-8f6b-4102-a954-c1ba79859adf-0
00:01:55.410 --> 00:01:57.130
Let's choose to edit it in Word
Online.

11abcd45-3f4b-4369-a0cf-13c267e3ad3d-0
00:01:58.290 --> 00:02:00.392
The great thing about
collaborating this way is that

11abcd45-3f4b-4369-a0cf-13c267e3ad3d-1
00:02:00.392 --> 00:02:02.811
everyone can see the changes
everyone else is making in real

11abcd45-3f4b-4369-a0cf-13c267e3ad3d-2
00:02:02.811 --> 00:02:03.010
time.

21d333e9-7bd7-4569-8606-8bd700ba03c1-0
00:02:03.930 --> 00:02:07.546
O If Jade adds some text to this
document and I switch back to my

21d333e9-7bd7-4569-8606-8bd700ba03c1-1
00:02:07.546 --> 00:02:11.053
coy of the document here in Word
on my computer, I can see that

21d333e9-7bd7-4569-8606-8bd700ba03c1-2
00:02:11.053 --> 00:02:14.231
change and I can see exactly
where Jade is working on the

21d333e9-7bd7-4569-8606-8bd700ba03c1-3
00:02:14.231 --> 00:02:17.410
document, which is indicated by
this colored cursor here.

f2b6a44f-cf8f-4e4b-96b2-25bbe4108ab0-0
00:02:17.950 --> 00:02:19.630
If I roll my mouse over it, I
can see her name.

62fa143e-5fec-4676-92c5-efc10ad0d630-0
00:02:20.430 --> 00:02:22.511
This is esecially useful if
there are multiple people

62fa143e-5fec-4676-92c5-efc10ad0d630-1
00:02:22.511 --> 00:02:23.630
working on the same document.

4e75773f-9b89-4f52-9b8a-3a3a4baec8ed-0
00:02:23.750 --> 00:02:25.977
You can see where everybody is
working in that particular

4e75773f-9b89-4f52-9b8a-3a3a4baec8ed-1
00:02:25.977 --> 00:02:26.630
document at once.

775b6225-e54e-42d9-bfe6-f21cad524fa8-0
00:02:27.350 --> 00:02:30.245
Also, everyone's changes are
automatically saved, so everyone

775b6225-e54e-42d9-bfe6-f21cad524fa8-1
00:02:30.245 --> 00:02:32.954
else is always working on the
most utodate version of the

775b6225-e54e-42d9-bfe6-f21cad524fa8-2
00:02:32.954 --> 00:02:36.036
document and that's how to share
and collaborate on a document in

775b6225-e54e-42d9-bfe6-f21cad524fa8-3
00:02:36.036 --> 00:02:36.270
Word.